  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose is to investigate the effect of oral doses of SLx-4090 over 14 days on subjects
      with high triglycerides.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      1. Serum triglycerides

        2. Serum lipids and lipoproteins

        3. Safety and tolerability
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
